Matriline; several clans in Kiriwina + these subdivided; Each clan has one impt. family which contributes paramount chief to island; clans have chiefs and one paramount chief – come from one family [underlined] (= aristocratic subclan); Malasi clan the most impt. in  Kiriwina & Tabalu the most impt. family. Many clans per village – a distribution throughout Trobriands; Each clan has 4 subclans except 1, which has 2.
